INSERT INTO labels (
                organization_id,
                project_id,
                origin_node_id,
                name,
                icon,
                color
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
            RETURNING
                id              AS "id!",
                organization_id AS "organization_id!",
                project_id      AS "project_id?",
                origin_node_id  AS "origin_node_id?",
                name            AS "name!",
                icon            AS "icon!",
                color           AS "color!",
                version         AS "version!",
                deleted_at      AS "deleted_at?",
                created_at      AS "created_at!",
                updated_at      AS "updated_at!"
